OL,4,Creveals aggressive brain cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAuthor Sophie Kinsella has revealed
OL,8,Fshe has been diagnosed with an
OL,9,Faggressive form of brain .
OL,11,FThe novelist, 54, real name Madeleine
OL,12,FSophie Wickham, is best known for her
OL,13,Fbestselling Shopaholic book series.
OL,15,FShe said she has been receiving
OL,16,Fchemotherapy and radiotherapy, writing
OL,17,Fon social media: "To my dear readers
OL,18,Fand followers. I've wanted for a long
OL,19,Ftime to share with you a health update
OL,20,Fand I've been waiting for the strength
OL,21,Fto do so.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/8
