OL,4,Creveals aggressive brain cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"At the end of 2022 I was diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith glioblastoma, a form of
OL,9,Faggressive brain cancer.
OL,11,F"I did not share this before because I
OL,12,Fwanted to make sure that my children
OL,13,Fwere able to hear and process the news
OL,14,Fin privacy and adapt to our 'new
OL,15,Fnormal'.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/8
