OL,3,CShopaholic author Sophie Kinsella
OL,4,Creveals aggressive brain cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"At the moment all is stable and I am
OL,8,Ffeeling generally very well, though I
OL,9,Fget very tired and my memory is even
OL,10,Fworse than it was before!
OL,12,F"I am so grateful to my family and
OL,13,Fclose friends who have been an
OL,14,Fincredible support to me, and to the
OL,15,Fwonderful doctors and nurses who have
OL,16,Ftreated me.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
