OL,3,CShopaholic author Sophie Kinsella
OL,4,Creveals aggressive brain cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"I am also so grateful to my readers
OL,8,Ffor your constant support. The
OL,9,Fwonderful response to The Burnout has
OL,10,Freally buoyed me up, during a
OL,11,Fdifficult time.
OL,13,F"To everyone who is suffering from
OL,14,Fcancer in any form I send love and
OL,15,Fbest wishes, as well as to those who
OL,16,Fsupport them.
OL,18,F"It can feel very lonely and scary to
OL,19,Fhave a tough diagnosis, and the
OL,20,Fsupport and care of those around you
OL,21,Fmeans more than words can say.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
