OL,7,F"I'll be in touch soon, and in the
OL,8,Fmeanwhile, greetings from sunny
OL,9,FLondon."
OL,11,FKinsella's latest book The Burnout was
OL,12,Freleased in October 2023. Her other
OL,13,Fhit books include Can You Keep A
OL,14,FSecret? and The Undomestic Goddess.
OL,16,FHer novels have sold more than 45
OL,17,Fmillion copies in 60 plus countries,
OL,18,Fand have been translated into more
OL,19,Fthan 40 languages.
