OL,7,FThe first two novels in her hit eight-
OL,8,Fbook Shopaholic series, The Secret
OL,9,FDreamworld Of A Shopaholic and
OL,10,FShopaholic Abroad, were adapted into
OL,11,Fthe film 2009 Confessions Of A
OL,12,FShopaholic, starring Isla Fisher.
OL,14,FFisher commented on Kinsella's
OL,15,FInstagram post, writing: "Sending you
OL,16,Fso much love and healing energy."
OL,18,FKinsella shares four sons and a
OL,19,Fdaughter with husband Henry Wickham.
